 fit nickel isotope production ratio to [57Ni/56Ni]=2.5+-1.1, which is\nstill somewhat high but is in agreement with gamma-ray observations and model\npredictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Aug 2014 02:30:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-27"}
