s, by subtracting either the\n${\\cal O}(g^2\\,a^2)$ contributions, or the complete (all orders in $a$)\none-loop lattice artifacts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Aug 2014 08:30:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-14"}
