 acting in this system during the high state. In the low\nstate, the emission lines are absent at all orbital phases indicating that\naccretion has completely switched-off and that XSSJ12270-4859 has transited\nfrom an accretion-powered to a rotation-powered phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Aug 2014 14:58:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Aug 2014 12:18:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
